	     <tr><td valign=top id=fs8 class=mform><span id=notbold>By:</span> <a href=poster.html?user=93845><span id=Sage>Arjaizen</span></a><br><b><span id=Sage>Sage</span></b><br><span id=notbold>197 posts<br><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Excellent [4.66]</td><td valign=top class=mform width=100%><p>Well friends, it's time to make it official:<br><br>As of this post, my fantasy writing days are most likely over.&nbsp;&nbsp;I've been playing Earth and Beyond for the past few months, and EQ only once since starting E&amp;B.  I can't really justify paying for a game I don't play (especially 2 accounts,) so my EQ days are done.  <br><br>Perhaps I'll find inspiration to write some Sci-fi based stories, but for obvious reasons, this isn't the appropriate forum for them.  <br><br>If you've read these stories and enjoyed them, then I'm thrilled what little talent I have has provided you with some entertainment.  If you've added your comments and/or encouragement to this journal, then you also have my profuse thanks for taking the time to write.<br><br>Fare well, my friends, and good hunting.</p>&nbsp;<br><span class=sm>----------------------------</span><br>Arjaizen Izrhume<br>40th Circle Wizard of Erudin<br>Fallen Wolves</td></tr>
