	     <tr><td id=headerrow colspan=2 class=mform valign=top><a name=/journal2.html?user=93845&mid=101232344134463>&nbsp;</a><a id=sj href=/journal2.html?user=93845&mid=101232344134463>RE: Missed your postings lately</a> <a id=fs8 href=/journal2.html?user=93845&mid=101232344134463#post><img src=http://everquest.allakhazam.com/static/reply.gif border=0 alt="Reply..." height=16 width=16></a>
