	     <tr><td valign=top id=fs8 class=mform><span id=notbold>By:</span> <a href=poster.html?user=120456><span id=Guru>QueenUsula</span></a><br><b><span id=Guru>Guru</span></b><br><span id=notbold>193 posts<br><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Good [4.49]</td><td valign=top class=mform width=100%><p>Greetings Arjaizen Izrhume,<br><br>It seems you have been unwise enough to side with that weak High Elf Icewind Novastorm, and his pathetic plots against the rulership of Pusbag and Ourself.&nbsp;&nbsp;<br>/ooc on<br>heh, it seems a lot of people are participatin now, interesting story is developing, so please keep posting, i need more victims<br>/ooc off<br>We warn you not to mettle in affairs beyond your scope of comprehension, and demand you withdraw any support you might have offered Our Elven cattle, upon pain of torture.  /cackle  Death is, afterall, a bit dull.</p>&nbsp;<br><span class=sm>----------------------------</span><br>Usula Wurmbane<br>Iksar Necromancer<br>Empress of Fear</td></tr>
